---
title: Beef Stroganoff with Peas and Mushrooms
description: This classic dish originated in Russia in the mid-19th century! Traditionally made with just beef and sour cream, we've gussied this dish up with the addition of hearty mushrooms and sweet green peas to make it extra yummy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/598c6bfda2882a21514759f2-aeee930b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/beef-stroganoff-fad8defe.pdf
servings: 2
